title: The Weekend Bite - Week Ending February 25th, 2022
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: This week we are joined by Susannah Streeter, Senior Investment and Markets Analyst at Hargreaves Lansdown. We discuss what the invasion means for global markets, the SWIFT payment system, inflation and interest rate hikes, and what investors need to watch in the coming weeks.
